    "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are a fast growing chain-stores retailer of ladies fashion footwear. Established in 2001, PAZZION caters to the modern, sophisticated trend-setter with an uncompromising standard for taste and quality. High-caliber craftsmanship and an unwavering attention to detail mean each pair of shoes is painstakingly designed to bring you the best in style and comfort. PAZZION is available in major retail malls across SINGAPORE with its flagship outlet at Wisma Atria Orchard Road. Internationally, PAZZION’s presence can be found in Brunei, Cambodia, Indonesia, Japan, Mauritius, South Korea, Thailand and Vietnam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Mission and Vision </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>PAZZION’s Vision is to establish itself as a recognizable international brand, known<br />\r\nfor its high-quality products that push the envelope of fashion trends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We aim to offer trendy, fashion-forward footwear and accessories with an<br />\r\nemphasis on quality, style and value. </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
